  "title": "罗永浩在用的数字人，拿下世界互联网大会科技大奖",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA4MTQ4NjQzMw==&mid=2652792139&idx=1&sn=eca3eb5b953f3ae4516681ba01913a80",
  "date": "2025-11-07 09:06:00",
  "author": "智东西",
  "siteName": "智东西",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>原创 <span>三北</span> <span>2025-11-07 17:06</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">浙江</span></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=580af93b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fz7ZD1WagSLh6sqjt21I4RK9m7EUnBpz9ib2qc5GytdBPrW9pjKbtVicJC0NwfbwJDdKzMHhtIBjqHFgYnsIEld6g%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p>成本降80%，转化率升31%：超拟真数字人成世界互联网大会 “红人”。</p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 20px;white-space: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"131\" data-ratio=\"0.23333333333333334\" style=\"width: 100% !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=42b50a63&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLgsRsrdDyQwMQFeic5uAcFg7nUPJuxZKtOOpVA2qEx77mXgLIZRcOIDgFRTT28ymhVVnUyawribP28g%2F640\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4255555555555556\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: top;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" data-w=\"900\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f3d881fd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLh6sqjt21I4RK9m7EUnBpz9Kg7eWLN5AN4qQSiaAZIhfFAggciaUeicKLtKYysC23Mc6udicQLNut1jQw%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">▲图片由AI生成</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin: 15px 8px 35px;\">\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: normal;font-size: 15px;padding: 0 10px;border-left: 3.5px solid #00b0ec;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">成本降80%，转化率升31%：超拟真数字人成世界互联网大会“红人”。</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin: 10px 8px 7.5px;white-space: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.75;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1.5px;text-align: right;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">作者 | &nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"display: inline-block;width: 63px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">三北</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 10px 8px 35px;white-space: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.75;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1.5px;text-align: right;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">编辑 | &nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"display: inline-block;width: 63px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">漠影</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">今年6月，罗永浩的数字人登上百度电商直播间，连续6小时不间断“带货”，一边调侃、一边拎着可乐、喝着奶茶，与助播朱萧木的数字人一唱一和，引发1300万人次围观。这场直播最终实现GMV（商品交易总额）5500万元，刷新了数字人带货纪录。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲罗永浩的数字人直播</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">现在，驱动这场直播的“AI总导演”，站上了世界互联网大会乌镇峰会的领奖台。</span></strong></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在11月6日至9日举行的2025年世界互联网大会乌镇峰会上，百度“</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">剧本驱动多模协同的高拟真数字人技术</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">”荣获</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">领先科技奖</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，实现连续三年获奖。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c37019a0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fz7ZD1WagSLh6sqjt21I4RK9m7EUnBpz9OpF2trxVlgYrBKe5y0vwU3PUrB9Nmpic58SUUPTmv1tR4mVOEuGl53w%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲百度CTO王海峰在讲解高拟真数字人技术</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从罗永浩的数字分身到世界互联网大会的领奖舞台，我们看到数字人好像跟前几年我们印象中的不一样了，</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">一个问题随之浮现：</span></strong></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">让数字人跨越“形似”的初级阶段，进入“神形兼备”的全新境界，百度是如何做的？</span></strong></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">01</span></em></strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;color: #00b0ec;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></em></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0.5px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">乌镇大会上的AI新风向：</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0.5px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">数字人成大模型经典落地场景</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">世界互联网大会“领先科技奖”是全球互联网科技发展的一个风向标。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在今年的世界互联网大会乌镇峰会上，评审委员会从34个国家和地区征集了424项科技成果，经海内外专家评审，最终遴选出17项年度领先成果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">其中，</span><strong><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><span leaf=\"\">作为融合了大语言模型与多模态技术的创新应用，百度“剧本驱动多模协同的高拟真数字人技术”成功入选。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">一同入选的还有中国科学院计算技术研究所、中国科学院软件研究所的“处理器芯片软硬件全自动设计”，清华大学“北斗三号卫星导航信号关键技术及应用”等成果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=38282129&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fz7ZD1WagSLh6sqjt21I4RK9m7EUnBpz9ibsf2k9S7gSYQHofQe14O2rzMK03nlqCXDJhkm33icI8MGZpBTA6ZDcg%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲2025年世界互联网大会领先科技奖颁奖现场</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">当下，数字人正成为AI最具代表性的落地场景之一。百度“剧本驱动多模协同的高拟真数字人技术”体现了这一趋势，不仅是语言、视觉、语音技术的融合创新，更是百度多年AI技术的集大成者。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从2023年“知识增强大语言模型关键技术”到2024年“文心智能体技术”，</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">百度成为唯一连续三年获奖的人工智能公司。</span></strong></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">02</span></em></strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;color: #00b0ec;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></em></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0.5px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">何以“高拟真”？5大核心技术</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0.5px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">为数字人注入“灵魂”</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">过去我们谈数字人，更多是关注“像不像”；而今天百度的数字人，已经进入“神似”的维度。</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">何以“高拟真”？</span></strong></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">其核心，在于以文心大模型为内核的“剧本驱动多模协同技术”，让数字人具备了自我理解、规划和表演的能力。</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">该技术有以下五大创新点：</span></strong></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.29791666666666666\" data-w=\"960\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d83f17e6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLh6sqjt21I4RK9m7EUnBpz98hpxVe6pCWvCJgDpBuocbtSw1ib1eibE30VicpM3JRQSsv7icOmsLMyTGg%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">1、剧本驱动多模协同：为数字人注入“灵魂”</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">传统数字人依赖人工脚本和单模态驱动，而百度的这项技术能生成一份真正意义上的“剧本”，剧本生成的核心在于语言模型驱动下的多模态协同，不仅有“说什么”，还有“怎么说、说的时候怎么配合动作表情”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">比如，当提到“法令纹”时，视觉系统会自动指向对应面部区域；当数字人“送福利”时，语音模块会自动调整语调，表现出兴奋情绪。甚至在双人互动时，还能标记“在哪个词后接话”，实现无缝对话。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这让数字人不再只是“说话的模型”，而是真正拥有导演级的多模态表达协调力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4552083333333333\" data-w=\"960\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=600ca7e1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLh6sqjt21I4RK9m7EUnBpz9jT8Z95HxibovWuibdYqOCQsYleCWXsa6RTHKwJO7lmfxxyufAW9Yh41w%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">2、融合多模规划与深度思考的剧本生成：让对话自然流畅</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">数字人不止能说台词，还能“思考剧情”。百度通过融合多模规划与大模型推理，实现了对对话上下文的整体理解。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在直播中，数字人不仅能按照预设剧本推进，还能根据直播间实时热度及用户反馈，智能调整讲解节奏与互动内容，实现衔接自然的动态交互。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这正是数字人老罗能秒接网络热梗，展现出鲜明人设与活泼语言风格的技术基础。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">3、动态决策的实时交互：赋予“临场反应”能力</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">基于大模型的实时感知与决策能力，数字人不再是单向输出的播报机器，而具备了类似真人的现场“判断力”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">它能够理解弹幕评论、感知直播间氛围，并据此做出实时反馈，如回答用户提问、玩梗互动、调整讲解策略，从而极大提升了互动的真实感与用户的参与感。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">4、文本自控的语音合成：告别“机械朗读”</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">声音，是数字人“灵魂”的另一半。百度的语音合成大模型通过“文本自控”机制，让声音摆脱机械朗读感，实现与表达与语义、情绪高度一致。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">其核心在于，模型能深度理解直播台词的文风与语境，并结合发音人（如罗永浩）的独特特征，将文本信息“翻译”成自然、富有感染力的声音。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">通过对话上下文编码器，百度解决了双人直播中声音配合的难题，实现了罗永浩与朱萧木数字人之间流畅、自然的对话效果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.45625\" data-w=\"960\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d7d1951d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLh6sqjt21I4RK9m7EUnBpz9uwygwvmYtHyicwt02GdSPtxW579ibl0bbGOdpKgjhx1JOicfxueictDQbw%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">5、高一致性超拟真长视频生成：挑战“时长极限”</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">数字人直播常常持续数小时，如何让其在长时间内保持表情、动作和场景的自然连贯，是一项行业难题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">百度通过结合多模态视频理解、跨模态信号生成等关键技术，攻克了高可控交互、长时间一致性保持等业界难题，实现了高一致性、超拟真的数字人长视频生成，将AI视频生成的应用边界从“秒级”拓展至“小时级”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">罗永浩数字人直播6小时全程动作自然、视线交互精准，就是这一技术的成果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">可以看到，百度以“</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">神、形、音、容、话</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">”的统一能力，构建一个兼具表达力与情感力的数字人系统。它不只是模仿人类，而是在理解人类表达逻辑的基础上“再创造人类体验”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">03</span></em></strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;color: #00b0ec;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></em></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0.5px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">从罗永浩到万千场景：</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0.5px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">10万数字人，让开播成本暴降80%</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">顶尖的技术价值，最终需要通过大规模应用与实实在在的商业效益来验证。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在百度，这项获奖技术的规模化落地已现成效。官方数据显示，基于该技术已生产超过</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">10万</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">个数字人，覆盖电商、教育、法律、健康等</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">数十个行业</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，助力商家</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">开播成本降低80%</span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\">，直播转化率提升31%。</span></strong></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">以“罗永浩数字人”为例</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，其6月15日的首秀不仅是技术实力的展示，更是一场成功的商业实践：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">整场直播持续6小时，AI调用知识库</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">1.3万次</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，生成</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">9.7万字</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">产品讲解内容，双数字人搭档做出超</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">8300个动作</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。从直播效果来看，整场直播吸引</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">1300万人次</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">观看，GMV突破</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">5500万元</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，部分核心品类</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">带货单量甚至超过罗永浩5月真人首秀同期数据。</span></strong></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">罗永浩本人也通过视频表示“让我惊讶”、“完美收官”，称数字人直播“可能代表了电商直播的新趋势”。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲罗永浩的数字人直播</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">技术红利正渗透至千行百业。</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">在山东德州夏津县，三位平均年龄超65岁的老支书，借助百度“慧播星”数字人技术，进行7×24小时不间断直播，精准讲解产品、实时回复问题。开通数字人直播短短</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">一个月</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，他们的地瓜直播间订单近万单，总销售额突破</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">15万元</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，成功售出农产品</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">3.3万斤</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">据悉，这种“真人+数字人”双轨模式已形成可复制的助农路径——百度电商“一村一品”项目通过“</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">慧播星</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">”等技术，累计帮助全国</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">1000多</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">户农民增收，商品交易总额</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">超2500万元</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">可以看到，从超头主播的直播间到田间地头的助农现场，百度数字人技术正在智能客服、虚拟教师、数字代言人、互动娱乐等多个领域落地开花。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">04</span></em></strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;color: #00b0ec;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></em></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0.5px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">结语：AI数字人迎技术产业升级</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0.5px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">带来商业新增长点</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从罗永浩直播间里那个能接梗、会互动、神形兼备的数字人，到赋能十万数字人降低商业成本、提升转化效率的产业平台，我们看到，以大模型为核心的AI数字人技术，已成为驱动产业升级、创造商业新增长点的强大引擎。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">数字人的发展，已走过“形似”、“神似”，正进入百度所定义的</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">“高拟真”、</span></span><span leaf=\"\">“高说服力”阶段。而未来，数字人或将真正在某些方面超越真人，实现超长待机、千人千面、多语言多风格的极致服务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">过去的十年，百度在AI上的每一次突破，都像是铺设通向未来的基石。世界互联网大会展现出的新风向表明，技术长期主义与系统化布局是推动智能产业发展的必由之路。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505287165\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2611111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7c797640&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fz7ZD1WagSLgtEXzbJAdOtc29yCc17rnZHpbsKeCVD1uH1AdBs7rPf30efSgMlmLJc6nfU4DIje70mPBia2iaTzVg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 25px;margin-left: 8px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;text-align: justify;letter-spacing: 0.544px;outline: none;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" data-style=\"margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 8px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 0.544px; outline: none; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" class=\"js_darkmode__24\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\" data-style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\" class=\"js_darkmode__25\"><span leaf=\"\">（本文系网易新闻•网易号特色内容激励计划签约账号【智东西】原创内容，未经账号授权，禁止随意转载。）</span></span><span leaf=\"\">\n    <br>\n   </span></p>\n  <hr style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;white-space: normal;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);height: 1px;clear: both;background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);transform-origin: 0px 0px;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\">\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"display:block;margin: 0 auto;margin-bottom:-10px;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0150300601202404\" data-w=\"998\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=759e9367&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLhpOqg6zOCwphX2keEz0hSgmzKkgeVMh3Ciagvr5XDqDljXvwVN2Her1PlpFMwTRCqGREKaStqTvdA%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, STHeiti, SimHei, sans-serif;\">\n   <div>\n    <div style=\"height: 0px;\">\n     <p style=\"padding-top: 0;opacity: 0.001;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;background-color: blue;\"><span leaf=\"\"><mp-common-profile class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"智东西\" data-alias=\"zhidxcom\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/z7ZD1WagSLg1QQZ9WhzKFpoX6M9OFR8lZIbyhXWlLeyDm8kcJHPOt2FibQeibbonAAYAPyaCwZ4Y0RborxHic3ryQ/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"智能产业第一媒体！智东西专注报道人工智能主导的前沿技术发展，和技术应用带来的千行百业产业升级。聚焦智能变革，服务产业升级。\" data-id=\"MzA4MTQ4NjQzMw==\"></mp-common-profile></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"10000\"></mp-style-type></p>\n  <p><a href=\"2652792139\">阅读原文</a></p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/link-proxy/?k=c9fd3b15&amp;r=1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%3F__biz%3DMzA4MTQ4NjQzMw%3D%3D%26mid%3D2652792139%26idx%3D1%26sn%3Deca3eb5b953f3ae4516681ba01913a80\">跳转微信打开</a></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "百度“剧本驱动多模协同高拟真数字人技术”荣获世界互联网大会大奖，显著降低商业成本并提升转化率。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "百度“剧本驱动多模协同高拟真数字人技术”荣获世界互联网大会大奖，显著降低商业成本并提升转化率。",
  "summary": "文章深入介绍了百度“剧本驱动多模协同的高拟真数字人技术”荣获世界互联网大会领先科技奖。该技术融合大语言模型与多模态能力，使数字人从“形似”迈向“神形兼备”，具备自我理解、规划和表演能力。以罗永浩数字人直播为例，该技术实现了 5500 万元 GMV，并宣称能将开播成本降低 80%，转化率提升 31%。文章详细阐述了五大核心创新点，包括剧本驱动多模协同、融合多模规划的剧本生成、动态决策的实时交互、文本自控的语音合成以及高一致性超拟真长视频生成。技术已广泛应用于电商、教育等数十个行业，生产超过 10 万个数字人，为产业升级带来新增长点。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "百度数字人技术通过“剧本驱动多模协同”实现“高拟真”",
      "explanation": "该技术以文心大模型为核心，整合语言、视觉、语音等多模态能力，使数字人具备自我理解、规划和表演能力，超越形似达到神形兼备。"
    },
    {
      "point": "技术在商业应用中展现出显著的成本效益和转化率提升",
      "explanation": "罗永浩数字人直播创下 5500 万元 GMV，该技术已帮助商家开播成本降低 80%，直播转化率提升 31%，具备强大的商业落地价值。"
    },
    {
      "point": "五大核心技术创新共同构建了数字人的“神、形、音、容、话”能力",
      "explanation": "包括剧本驱动多模协同、深度思考剧本生成、动态实时交互、文本自控语音合成及高一致性长视频生成，全面提升数字人表现力。"
